headline: All You Need to Know About Wabtec (WAB) Rating Upgrade to Buy
summary: Wabtec (WAB) has been upgraded to a Zacks Rank #2 (Buy), reflecting growing optimism about the company's earnings prospects. This might drive the stock higher in the near term.

headline: 2 Cash-Producing Stocks on Our Watchlist and 1 We Ignore
summary: Generating cash is essential for any business, but not all cash-rich companies are great investments. Some produce plenty of cash but fail to allocate it effectively, leading to missed opportunities.
